ligues_value = data[["Ligue", "Value"]].groupby(['Ligue'],
               as_index=False).median().sort_values(by='Value', ascending=False)
In[10]:
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))

sns.barplot(x = 'Value', y = 'Ligue',

In[11]:
ligue_nationalities_values = ligues_value.merge(nations_value, left_on='Ligue', right_on='Nationality',
                             suffixes=('_ligue', '_nationality'))
In[12]:
ligue_nationalities_values.drop('Ligue', axis=1, inplace=True)
In[13]:
ligue_nationalities_values['Difference'] = (ligue_nationalities_values['Value_ligue'] - ligue_nationalities_values["Value_nationality"])
In[14]:
ligue_nationalities_values.sort_values('Difference', inplace=True)
In[15]:
ligue_nationalities_values = ligue_nationalities_values.melt(id_vars = 'Nationality')
In[16]:
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 15))

ligues_nationalities_values_plot = sns.barplot(x = 'value', y = 'Nationality',
                                data = ligue_nationalities_values, 
                                hue='variable')
In[17]:
ligues_melt = data[['Ligue','log_Value']].melt(id_vars =['log_Value'], var_name = 'Level', value_name = 'Country')
In[18]:
nationalities_melt = data[['Nationality', 'log_Value']].melt(id_vars =['log_Value'], var_name = 'Level', value_name = 'Country')
In[19]:
ligues_nationalities = pd.concat([ligues_melt, nationalities_melt])
In[20]:
top_10_ligues = ligues_nationalities['Country'].value_counts().head(10).index.to_list()
In[21]:
ligues_order = ligues_value[ligues_value.Ligue.isin(top_10_ligues)].Ligue.to_list()
In[22]:
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 15))
ligues_plot = sns.boxplot(
    y = 'Country',
    x = 'log_Value', 
    data = ligues_nationalities[ligues_nationalities.Country.isin(top_10_ligues)],
    hue='Level',
    palette='hls',
    order = ligues_order)
